# Video Studio Design System

Full spec: `docs/design-system/video-studio.md`  
Tokens: `components/genbar/genBarStyles.ts`, `components/video/videoStudioTokens.ts`  
Styles: `components/video/videoTheme.css` (scoped under `.video-studio`)

## Must use

- `GEN_BAR_R` (6px), `GEN_BAR_FORM`, `GEN_BAR_CHIP`, `GEN_BAR_GENERATE` for controls
- `vs-*` classes from `videoTheme.css` — never duplicate styles inline
- CSS variables: `--ink`, `--primary`, `--border-soft`, `--surface-muted`, `--card-light`

## Layout rules

- Left: `vs-sidebar` (max 320px). Right: `vs-workspace`
- Default right content: «История» / «Как это работает» — **no model bar**
- «Сменить» opens `VideoPresetPicker` as **full workspace replacement**, not overlay
- Gallery panel uses same surface as sidebar (`GEN_BAR_FORM` look: card-light + border + 6px radius)

## Sidebar order

`vs-mode-tabs` → `vs-preset-card` → `vs-model-row` (after gallery pick) → `vs-frames` → `vs-prompt-block` → `vs-sidebar__dock` (params + generate)

## UX state

- `presetPanelUsed === false`: hide model name, model row, audio badges
- `presetPanelUsed === true`: show preset + model on card, `vs-model-row`, audio toggles if `variant.hasAudio`
- Model list only inside `VideoPresetPicker`, not on static workspace

## Prompt controls

- Badges **inside** `vs-prompt-block` (`vs-prompt-badge`), not a separate row
- Enhance: «Улучшение вкл.» / «Выкл.»
- Audio (audio models only): «Звук вкл.» / «Без звука» → `videoGenerateAudio` in App

## Presets

- All models: «Обычная Генерация» (`DEFAULT_VIDEO_PRESET`)
- Extra presets: Seedance models only (`getPresetsForModel`)
- Picking preset in gallery sets preset **and** model tier/variant

## Forbidden

- Horizontal divider strips (`border-t`/`border-b`) between sidebar sections or under model tabs
- Arbitrary border-radius (except 12px preset cards in gallery)
- Model names on main workspace before gallery selection
- Dropdown menus clipped by `overflow: hidden` on sidebar — use `vs-sidebar__dock` + upward `GEN_BAR_DROPDOWN`

## New components checklist

1. Read `docs/design-system/video-studio.md`
2. Add styles to `videoTheme.css` under `.video-studio`
3. Use tokens from `videoStudioTokens.ts` / `genBarStyles.ts`
4. Verify dropdowns and mobile 375px
